MEDICAL DISCLAIMER

This software is provided for informational and educational purposes only. 
MedIntelOS is a software framework and does not constitute medical advice, 
diagnosis, or treatment. Any clinical decision support outputs generated by 
this system are intended solely as adjunct tools to assist qualified healthcare 
professionals.

Healthcare organizations deploying this software are solely responsible for:
1. Ensuring compliance with applicable laws and regulations in their jurisdiction
2. Validating AI/ML models against their local patient populations before clinical use
3. Maintaining appropriate clinical oversight of all AI-generated recommendations
4. Obtaining necessary regulatory approvals (FDA, CE Mark, etc.) for clinical deployment
5. Training clinical staff on appropriate and safe use of the software

AI outputs must NEVER replace the clinical judgment of qualified healthcare 
professionals. All patient care decisions remain the responsibility of the 
treating clinician.

The authors and contributors of MedIntelOS shall not be held liable for any 
clinical decisions made based on the outputs of this software.
